svg.title: Sheet Music for "Blackbird Hornpipe (2)"

text.tspan: Source: From a version performed by Padraig McGovern and Peter Carberry, originally in B.
Notes: This is another version of the Blackbird Hornpipe that is clearly related to the first version
I transcribed. This is a little more repetitive, but in a good way! Perhaps good as a reference.
